Question (1): 
start word: FIRE
ending word: SNOW
```
Deque<List<Integer>> queue = new LinkedList<>();
queue.add(List.of("FIRE"));

while (!queue.isEmpty()) {
 List<Integer> path = queue.pop();
 String startWord = path.get(path.size() - 1);

 if (startWord.equals("SNOW")) {
 return true;
 }

 for (String endWord : words) {
 // Compare two words letter by letter to see if they're only one letter difference
 if (compare(startWord, endWord)) {
 List<Integer> newPath = new ArrayList<>(path);
 newPath.add(endWord);
 queue.add(newPath);
 }
 }

 return false;
}
```
